column2: SELECT Top #   g.objID, g.ra,g.dec, y.z, g.petroMag_u, g.petroMag_g, g.petroMag_r, g.petroMag_i, g.petroMag_z, j.H_beta_flux, j.oiii_#_flux, j.H_alpha_flux, j.NII_#_flux,    j.sigma_balmer,j.spectofiber,j.h_alpha_eqw  into mydb.BL_test2 from galaxy g      left outer join specobj y ON y.specobjID = g.specobjID       left outer join emissionlinesport h ON h.specobjID = g.specobjID      join galspecline j ON j.specobjID = g.specobjID
